      "id": 807183,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "Title: SQL Injection in Structure Plugin\nVulnerability: An SQL injection flaw was discovered in ExpressionEngine's Structure plugin, specifically in the delete_channels() function. User input from the channel_ids parameter is passed directly into SQL queries without proper sanitization. Although the vulnerability requires admin panel access, a limited-privilege admin could exploit it ",
